<th colspan="2" class="fn" style="text-align:center; background-color:gold; font-size:120%;"><i>Saint Jerome</i></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;">
<div class="center">
<div class="floatnone"><a href="/wiki/File:Durer-jerome.jpg" class="image" title="Durer-jerome.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0c/Durer-jerome.jpg/200px-Durer-jerome.jpg" width="200" height="267" border="0" /></a></div>
