<li id="cite_note-fraud-26">^ <a href="#cite_ref-fraud_26-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-fraud_26-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.jstor.org/stable/1584340?seq=1&amp;Search=yes&amp;term=Seneca&amp;term=Pythagoras&amp;term=Jerome&amp;term=ac&amp;list=hide&amp;searchUri=%2Faction%2FdoBasicSearch%3FQuery%3DJerome%2BPythagoras%2Bac%2BSeneca%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26wc%3Don&amp;item=3&amp;ttl=107&amp;returnArticleService=showArticle&amp;resultsServiceName=doBasicResultsFromArticle" class="external text" title="http://www.jstor.org/stable/1584340?seq=1&amp;Search=yes&amp;term=Seneca&amp;term=Pythagoras&amp;term=Jerome&amp;term=ac&amp;list=hide&amp;searchUri=%2Faction%2FdoBasicSearch%3FQuery%3DJerome%2BPythagoras%2Bac%2BSeneca%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26wc%3Don&amp;item=3&amp;ttl=107&amp;returnArticleService=showArticle&amp;resultsServiceName=doBasicResultsFromArticle" rel="nofollow">"Jerome: The "Vir Trilinguis" and the "Hebraica Veritas""</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.jstor.org/stable/1584340?seq=1&amp;Search=yes&amp;term=Seneca&amp;term=Pythagoras&amp;term=Jerome&amp;term=ac&amp;list=hide&amp;searchUri=%2Faction%2FdoBasicSearch%3FQuery%3DJerome%2BPythagoras%2Bac%2BSeneca%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26wc%3Don&amp;item=3&amp;ttl=107&amp;returnArticleService=showArticle&amp;resultsServiceName=doBasicResultsFromArticle" class="external free" title="http://www.jstor.org/stable/1584340?seq=1&amp;Search=yes&amp;term=Seneca&amp;term=Pythagoras&amp;term=Jerome&amp;term=ac&amp;list=hide&amp;searchUri=%2Faction%2FdoBasicSearch%3FQuery%3DJerome%2BPythagoras%2Bac%2BSeneca%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26wc%3Don&amp;item=3&amp;ttl=107&amp;returnArticleService=showArticle&amp;resultsServiceName=doBasicResultsFromArticle" rel="nofollow">http://www.jstor.org/stable/1584340?seq=1&amp;Search=yes&amp;term=Seneca&amp;term=Pythagoras&amp;term=Jerome&amp;term=ac&amp;list=hide&amp;searchUri=%2Faction%2FdoBasicSea